  "title": "Repository caching invariants and worktree list mutation",
  "summary": "Repository<Arc<RepoCache>> caches read-only values to avoid re-querying git. Mutating paths (switch --create / remove) must NOT read list_worktrees() through the same Repository after their own mutation - cache is now stale. Per CLAUDE.md, dirty/HEAD must NOT be cached. Stale cache reads here surface as missing worktrees or wrong commit in hook template vars.",
